items.headline: AN INTRODUCTION TO THE WONDERFUL WORLD OF DIFFERENT TOPICS UNDER ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE LAW
objectives_summary: This course enables a person to have a holistic perspective of some of the important issues and topics that are gaining significance in the evolving Artificial Intelligence Law discipline. This course would sensitize the students about the importance of ethical principles and standards in Artificial Intelligence Law, the need for protecting and preserving the individuals’ data and personal privacy, need for enabling data protection in the Artificial Intelligence paradigm, the relationship between cyber security and Artificial Intelligence and the emerging need of regulating Artificial Intelligence cybercrimes.   After completing this course, the students would have a better understanding of how Artificial Intelligence Law is evolving, with the maturing of Artificial Intelligence.
Artificial Intelligence Law, Artificial Intelligence and Ethics, AI and Privacy, AI and Data Protection, AI and Cybercrimes, AI and Cybersecurity
